{"id": 1984, "date": "1987-03-15T11:00:38", "date_gmt": "1987-03-15T19:00:38", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1984"}, "modified": "2026-06-09T17:09:00", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-10T00:09:00", "slug": "matr-bruce-springsteen-joe-ely-arlo-guthrie-indigo-girls-and-more-ive-got-to-know", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/03/15/matr-bruce-springsteen-joe-ely-arlo-guthrie-indigo-girls-and-more-ive-got-to-know/", "title": {"rendered": "I&#8217;ve Got to Know"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>On September 29, 1996, Bruce joined a stellar roster of musicians on stage at Cleveland&#8217;s Severance Hall to pay tribute to Woody Guthrie.</p>\n<p>Among the tracks performed that night: Woody&#8217;s &#8220;I&#8217;ve Got to Know,&#8221; featuring contributions by Bruce, Joe Ely, Arlo Guthrie, The Indigo Girls, Ani DiFranco, Billy Bragg, Country Joe McDonald, David Pirner, and Ramblin&#8217; Jack Elliott.</p>\n<p>This is the only time Bruce is known to have performed this song.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0G8dDlLkG7c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Here&#8217;s the original for comparison:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/A_f1nlorvU0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>I&#8217;ve Got to Know</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> September 29, 1996 (Cleveland, OH)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> September 29, 1996 (Cleveland, OH)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 May 7, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>A host of artists join Bruce in paying tribute to Woody Guthrie in this performance from 1996.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69816, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [4, 3617, 5], "tags": [919, 918, 920, 69, 921, 922, 917, 141, 923, 270], "class_list": ["post-1984", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-cover-me", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-ani-difranco", "tag-arlo-guthrie", "tag-billy-bragg", "tag-cleveland", "tag-country-joe-mcdonald", "tag-david-pirner", "tag-indigo-girls", "tag-joe-ely", "tag-ramblin-jack-elliott", "tag-woody